316
00:38:17,760 --> 00:38:22,160
<i>La fantasia diventerà realtà</i>

317
00:38:22,680 --> 00:38:25,480
<i>È la casa dirimpetto</i>

318
00:38:25,840 --> 00:38:28,320
<i>Non tardare, io t'aspetto</i>

319
00:38:28,400 --> 00:38:33,560
<i>Ce la spasseremo a volontà</i>

320
00:38:36,000 --> 00:38:39,640
